{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Datebase/migration-reset","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c43a2abd-3ea2-5f97-b25e-bb4329cab33c","html":"<p>django.db.migrations.exceptions.NodeNotFoundError 에러는 마이그레이션을 초기화 해야 해결할 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"initpy를-제외한-모든-migration파일-제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#initpy%EB%A5%BC-%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8%ED%95%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%A0-migration%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"initpy를 제외한 모든 migration파일 제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>init</strong>.py를 제외한 모든 migration파일 제거</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">find</span> <span class=\"token operator\">.</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token builtin\">path</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"*/migrations/*.py\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>not <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>name <span class=\"token string\">\"__init__.py\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">delete</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">find</span> <span class=\"token operator\">.</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token builtin\">path</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"*/migrations/*.pyc\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">delete</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"스키마-생성